{
  "texts": [
    "The structure of LSTM-CNN can be seen in Fig. 5b.",
    "The detailed layers and parameters of this model are presented in Table A1.",
    "CNN-with-LSTM is a model that employs the parallel combination of both CNN and LSTM, merging their outputs through concatenation, and uses a fully connected network for regression analysis.",
    "By combining the feature extraction capabilities of CNN with the time series memory ability of LSTM, this model captures both the local and global temporal characteristics of the input data.",
    "This kind of hybrid structure has been used in soil moisture prediction and achieved satisfactory results (Yu et al., 2021)."
  ]
}